截至2020年，[[SpaceX|SpaceX]]運營著四個發射設施：[[卡納維爾角空軍基地40號航太發射複合體|卡納維爾角空軍基地40號航太發射複合體]]（SLC-40）、[[范登堡空軍基地太空發射複合體4|范登堡空軍基地太空發射複合體4]]E（SLC-4E）、[[甘迺迪航天中心39號發射台|甘迺迪航天中心39號發射台]]（LC-39A）和[[SpaceX南德克薩斯發射場|SpaceX南德克薩斯發射場]]。2016年9月的[[Amos-6|Amos-6]]事故損壞了40號太空發射場，修復工作於2017年12月完成。<ref name="sfn170913">{{cite web|url=https://spaceflightnow.com/2017/09/13/launch-operators-expect-minimal-delays-from-hurricane-irma/|title=Launch operators expect minimal delays from Hurricane Irma – Spaceflight Now|website=spaceflightnow.com|access-date=2017-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171018125836/https://spaceflightnow.com/2017/09/13/launch-operators-expect-minimal-delays-from-hurricane-irma/|archive-date=2017-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>SpaceX相信，通過將發射任務劃分為以下四個發射設施，他們可以優化發射操作並降低發射成本：用於[[NASA|NASA]]發射的LC-39A，用於[[美國空軍|美國空軍]]國家安全發射的SLC-40，用於繞極軌道的SLC-4E和南德克薩斯發射場，用於商業發射。<ref name=sfn20131018/>

首席運營官[[格溫妮·肖特韋爾|格溫妮·肖特韋爾]]（Gwynne Shotwell）在2014年表示，“我們在所有地點都在擴張”，“最終您會看到很多SpaceX發射場，以滿足我們預期的未來需求。” <ref name=tss20140321a>{{cite AV media |people=Gwynne Shotwell |date=2014-03-21 |title=Broadcast 2212: Special Edition, interview with Gwynne Shotwell |medium=audio file |url=http://archived.thespaceshow.com/shows/2212-BWB-2014-03-21.mp3 |accessdate=2014-03-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322013556/http://archived.thespaceshow.com/shows/2212-BWB-2014-03-21.mp3 |archivedate=2014-03-22 |format=mp3 |time=49:50–50:40 |publisher=The Space Show |id=2212 |quote= |dead-url=yes }}</ref>截至2016年6月， SpaceX討論了初步計劃，即在2019年以後每年平均發射90枚火箭。<ref name=fox35_2016062>{{cite news |url=http://www.fox35orlando.com/news/local-news/164663415-story |title=Port Commissioner: SpaceX negotiating Port lease to refurbish rocket boosters |work=Fox35 Local News |date=2016-06-23 |accessdate=2016-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160626135356/http://www.fox35orlando.com/news/local-news/164663415-story |archive-date=2016-06-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>SpaceX表示，根據市場需求，除[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]的位置外，他們實際上可能還需要另一個商業發射場。<ref name=sfn20131018/>

2016年，SpaceX簽署了一項為期五年的租約，以使用[[卡納維拉爾港|卡納維拉爾港]]53,000平方英尺（4,900平方米）的舊Spacehab大樓。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.floridatoday.com/story/tech/science/space/spacex/2016/11/23/spacex-plans-five-year-lease-complex-port-canaveral/94231520/ |title=SpaceX plans five-year lease of Port Canaveral complex |date=2016-11-23 |author=Dave Berman |newspaper=Florida Today |accessdate=2017-06-15 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128115456/https://www.floridatoday.com/story/tech/science/space/spacex/2016/11/23/spacex-plans-five-year-lease-complex-port-canaveral/94231520/ }}</ref>還計劃在附近建造新建築物，這些設施將用於翻新火箭。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theverge.com/2016/8/24/12627520/spacex-falcon-9-rockets-refurbish-port-canaveral-lease |title=SpaceX is building new facilities at Port Canaveral to refurbish rockets |date=2016-08-24 |author=Nick Statt |website=The Verge |accessdate=2017-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170402095248/http://www.theverge.com/2016/8/24/12627520/spacex-falcon-9-rockets-refurbish-port-canaveral-lease |archive-date=2017-04-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

此外，SpaceX還使用[[亞軌道|亞軌道]]測試設施，即[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]的SpaceX Rocket開發和測試設施。[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]正在建設一個高空亞軌道測試設施，<ref name=sfn20131018/>但在轉為商業飛行任務的飛行測試後被廢棄了。

SpaceX表示，他們認為目前正在使用或正在建設的四個軌道設施中的每一個都有一個利基市場，並且他們有足夠的發射業務來填滿每個墊塊，<ref name=sn20130802>{{cite news |last=Klotz |first=Irene |title=SpaceX Appetite for U.S. Launch Sites Grows |url=http://www.spacenews.com/article/launch-report/36587spacex-appetite-for-us-launch-sites-grows |accessdate=2013-09-05 |newspaper=Space News |date=2013-08-02 |archive-date=2013-09-05 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130905165354/http://www.spacenews.com/article/launch-report/36587spacex-appetite-for-us-launch-sites-grows }}</ref>尤其是到十年末，如果SpaceX業務保持強勁。<ref name=sfn20131018/>

==卡納維爾角空軍基地==
[[File:COTS_2_Falcon_launches.jpg|thumb]] Flight 3。]]
2007年，美國空軍將[[卡納維爾角空軍基地40號航太發射複合體|卡納維爾角空軍基地40號航太發射複合體]]（SLC-40）租賃給SpaceX，以發射[[獵鷹9號|獵鷹9號]]火箭。<ref name="FloridaToday">{{cite web |url=http://www.floridatoday.com/floridatoday/blogs/spaceteam/2007/04/spacex-cleared-for-cape-launches.html |title=SpaceX cleared for Cape launches |work=Florida Today |first=John |last=Kelly |date=2007-04-25 |accessdate=2010-06-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930030616/http://www.floridatoday.com/floridatoday/blogs/spaceteam/2007/04/spacex-cleared-for-cape-launches.html |archivedate=2007-09-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2008年4月，開始了支持SpaceX Falcon 9火箭發射所必需的地面設施的建設。改造包括安裝新的[[液氧|液氧]]和[[煤油|煤油]]罐以及建造用於火箭和有效載荷準備的機庫。

第一架獵鷹9號火箭於2008年末到達SLC-40，並於2009年1月10日首次架起。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.spacex.com/press.php?page=20090112 |title=SpaceX's Falcon 9 on Launch Pad at Cape Canaveral |work=SpaceX.com |first=Emily |last=Shanklin |date=2009-01-12 |accessdate=2010-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090201235841/http://spacex.com/press.php?page=20090112 |archive-date=2009-02-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>它於2010年6月4日首次發射升空，並搭載了一個虛擬有效載荷鑑定裝置，成功進入了軌道。為了支持獵鷹9號 v1.1運載火箭的發射，SpaceX在2013年對其發射台進行了修改，這是重型火箭的60％，重新對準的發動機<ref name=121117SFNfalcon9commercial>{{cite web |title=Falcon 9's commercial promise to be tested in 2013 |url=http://spaceflightnow.com/news/n1211/17f9customers/#.UKfUruQ0V8E |publisher=Spaceflight Now |accessdate=2012-11-17 |website= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121120010459/http://www.spaceflightnow.com/news/n1211/17f9customers/#.UKfUruQ0V8E |archive-date=2012-11-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>的推力比v1.0版本高60％，油箱長60％獵鷹9號戰艦，需要改裝的運輸車/豎立飛機。<ref name=sn20130906>{{cite news |last=Klotz |first=Irene |title=Musk Says SpaceX Being "Extremely Paranoid" as It Readies for Falcon 9’s California Debut |url=http://www.spacenews.com/article/launch-report/37094musk-says-spacex-being-%E2%80%9Cextremely-paranoid%E2%80%9D-as-it-readies-for-falcon-9%E2%80%99s |accessdate=2013-09-13 |newspaper=Space News |date=2013-09-06 |archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20130922163105/http://www.spacenews.com/article/launch-report/37094musk-says-spacex-being-%E2%80%9Cextremely-paranoid%E2%80%9D-as-it-readies-for-falcon-9%E2%80%99s |archive-date=2013-09-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年9月，獵鷹9號火箭在液氧裝填期間爆炸，為熱火試驗做準備時，該墊子受損。<ref>{{cite news |title=SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket, satellite destroyed in explosion |url=http://www.floridatoday.com/story/tech/science/space/spacex/2016/09/01/explosion-reported-spacex-pad/89710076/ |work=Florida Today |access-date=2016-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160902073133/http://www.floridatoday.com/story/tech/science/space/spacex/2016/09/01/explosion-reported-spacex-pad/89710076/ |archive-date=2016-09-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>自2017年12月[[SpaceX_CRS-13|SpaceX CRS-13]]任務爆炸發生以來，該墊塊首次得到維修和使用。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nasaspaceflight.com/2017/12/slc-40-comes-back-with-crs-13-static-fire/|title=SLC-40 comes back to life with CRS-13 static fire campaign|last=Gebhardt|first=Chris|date=2017-12-06|work=|access-date=2018-11-15|publisher=[[NASASpaceFlight.com|NASASpaceFlight.com]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180808130142/https://www.nasaspaceflight.com/2017/12/slc-40-comes-back-with-crs-13-static-fire/|archive-date=2018-08-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

